Class ChebiVertex

java.lang.Object
  net.sourceforge.metware.binche.graph.ChebiVertex

public class ChebiVertex
extends Object

Vertex of the ChebiGraph, which is used to store the result of the enrichment analysis in a graph based structure.

Author:
Stephan Beisken, Pablo Moreno
